      "instruction": "<p><strong>Preheat</strong> the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p><strong>Boil</strong> the kettle (used in steps 2 and 4)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cut</strong> the aubergine<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> in half lengthways</p>\r\n<p><strong>Score</strong> the flesh quite deeply (in a diamond pattern) taking care not to cut through the skin</p>",
